@startuml grace-convergence-sequence
' Standard UML theme (default colours/shapes).
skinparam dpi 300
title Feedback control: grace <-> convergence <-> probe

participant "Deployment\ncontroller" as DC
participant "Grace-convergence\ncontroller" as CC
participant "Membership layer\n(libcluster)" as LC
participant "Registry & handoff\n(Horde)" as H
participant "pod / kubelet" as P

DC -> CC: rolling update starting
CC -> LC: current convergence time?
LC --> CC: ~X s
CC -> H: pending handoff backlog / throughput?
H --> CC: N processes, R/s
CC -> CC: grace = f(backlog, convergence)
CC -> DC: set terminationGracePeriodSeconds\n+ pace maxUnavailable
DC -> P: SIGTERM (adequate grace)
P -> H: drain + hand off
H --> P: handoff complete (within grace)
note over P: no SIGKILL mid-handoff\n=> no state loss
@enduml
